  <acronym>TOKU</acronym>
  <official_title>Ureteropelvic Junction Obstruction in Early Childhood: Comparison of Surgical Therapy and Surveillance in Children With Scintigraphically Prooved Obstruction. A Prospective, Randomized, Controlled Multi-Center Study</official_title>
